response.overview: Ma Shwe and her husband Ko Tun work as servants in the house of rich folks Ko Thawtar and Ma Nwet.  Ma Ma Nwet loves to show off but she's very stingy. So they often laugh about her behind her back. One day, Ma Nwet gave Ma Shwe movie tickets. Not the cheap seats, but first-class, the kind meant for high society. What could possibly go wrong when they went to watch a movie in first class…
response.title: 1st class
